MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-1896. State ex rel. Orr v. Trimble.

Franklin County, No. 94APD06-928. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective October 12, 1995.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
